1015
01:05:35.860 --> 01:05:37.028
Bonjour, Ernest.

1016
01:05:37.570 --> 01:05:38.780
Dr Ernest Jones.

1017
01:05:38.780 --> 01:05:40.448
Jack Lewis. Enchanté.

1018
01:05:40.448 --> 01:05:42.158
